profile:
At WATERMAN, 95% of our business is referral. Most of our work comes directly from contractors. Cut out the middle man by calling us today to receive contractor rates.  
 
There are a lot of things we could tell you about ourselves, and how we became the best company to call when you’re dealing with a drain back up in Toronto. We can begin by telling you that we began as a plumber to other plumbers – stepping in to subcontract on projects when other professionals ran into a drain back up in that they couldn’t handle on their own. The dozens of plumbing companies we work with have been so impressed with us, that they have used us again and again as the experts for repairs to drains, flooded basements, and even sewer back ups.
 
Roto-rooter, camera inspection of drainage system. Thermal image inspection of foundation leaks. Drain flushing. Pipe burst. Torpedo services. Foundations. Waterproofing. Plumbing repairs and installations. Basement Lowering, Sewer Backup, 24 hour emergency service
 
But of course, it’s hard to keep a service like ours secret for very long. We quickly started to gain a reputation as the business to deal with for a drain back up in Toronto.

profile:
Taking care of a property can feel like a full-time job. From regular maintenance to emergency services, it can be difficult to keep up, particularly for a multi-unit or commercial property. Worse than not having time to tackle seasonal and routine chores, improper techniques can lead to damage. Ditch unnecessary wear, tear and breakage by trusting professional property maintenance services.

It is easy for property owners to spot certain issues outside, particularly when it comes to lawn care or a landscaping service. While lawn maintenance is important, so is the overall condition of your structures and surrounding areas. Regular cleaning not only leaves structures looking their best but it can also help to get the full lifespan out of your construction materials.

THE BENEFITS OF PROFESSIONAL PROPERTY SERVICES
Plenty of property owners are happy to off-load some of their workload onto a pro, just to free up their schedules. While having a bit more spare time is great, expert care can actually protect construction materials, saving money on premature replacements or costly repairs, all while keeping a safe environment for guests and tenants.

When dirt and debris sits against surfaces, it can wear down even the toughest of materials. From vinyl siding, roof decks and even concrete – nothing is safe from the elements. Each area of your property will be hit differently by dirt, moisture and dampness or invasive growth, so your cleaning techniques should change alongside them.

Taking a heavy-handed approach to vulnerable materials can result in serious damage. Treating something like moss growth with a wire brush and elbow grease can mean stripping way protective coatings and creating entry points for water. This means you can expect damage, leaks and rot. Trusting an expert for regular care and moss control services mean getting the best results, every time.

GOING GORILLA FOR YOUR PROPERTY SERVICES
Choosing the right maintenance company in Vaughan can be tough. With so many options, it can be difficult to narrow the search, but our Gorillas have got you covered. With years of experience under our belts, our highly trained technicians have seen and done it all! Fully insured staff help to protect homeowners from liability issues while top-notch safety equipment keeps our technicians safe.
